GAAG,cAAc,CAAC;QACrI,IAAI,CAAC,iBAAiB,CAAC,qBAAqB,GAAG,SAAS,GAAG,IAAI,CAAC,iBAAiB,CAAC,qBAAqB,CAAC;IAC1G,CAAC;IAED;;OAEG;IACK,sBAAsB;QAC5B,OAAO;YACL,WAAW,EAAE,CAAC,SAA8B,EAAE,EAAE;gBAC9C,mDAAmD;gBACnD,OAAO,CAAC,CAAC,MAAM,CAAC;oBACd,EAAE,EAAE,CAAC,CAAC,MAAM,EAAE;oBACd,KAAK,EAAE,CAAC,CAAC,GAAG,EAAE,CAAC,QAAQ,EAAE;oBACzB,OAAO,EAAE,CAAC,CAAC,OAAO,EAAE,CAAC,OAAO,CAAC,IAAI,CAAC;iBACnC,CAAC,CAAC;YACL,CAAC;YACD,cAAc,EAAE,CAAC,UAAiC,EAAE,EAAE;gBACpD,4BAA4B;gBAC5B,OAAO,UAAU,CAAC,GAAG,CAAC,GAAG,CAAC,EAAE,CAAC,IAAI,CAAC,sBAAsB,EAAE,CAAC,WAAW,CAAC,GAAG,CAAC,CAAC,CAAC;YAC/E,CAAC;SACF,CAAC;IACJ,CAAC;CACF;AAED,OAAO,EAAE,sBAAsB,EAAE,CAAC",
